<ul>
<li><a href = "../iwg/IWGrept.html">Interactive Working Group Report To Senator Leahy</a>
<p>
<ul>The Interactive Working Group is a coalition of public interest and industry representatives concerned with government content regulations in interactive media. This report was completed at the request of Senator Leahy and describes currently available parental control technologies, the state of current law, and the constitutional issues raised by content regulations in new media.</ul></ul>
