Contacts:

Center for Democracy and Technology: (v) +1.202.637.9800
 Jerry Berman, Executive Director        (jberman@cdt.org)
 Daniel Weitzner, Deputy Director        (djw@cdt.org)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

(2) NEW CDT SYSOP/ONLINE PRESENCE -- BOB PALACIOS (bobpal@cdt.org)

CDT welcomes Bob Palacios, as our new sysop/net-presence. Bob comes to 
CDT from People for the American Way where he was systems 
administrator/webmaster. 

Jonah Seiger, CDT's Policy Analyst, who has been moonlighting as sysop, will 
be shifting his attention to concentrate full time on policy work. Jonah will 
continue to maintain a high visibility on the net and will continue to work 
on online organizing and net.campaigns, but his focus will be on strategic and 
tactical issues while Bob will handle the technical and day to day details.

Bob's immediate role will be to manage and maintain our online presence, 
maintain our World Wide Web and ftp servers, cultivate new outlets for 
CDT on the net, develop relationships with other, untapped friendly online 
organizations and individuals to enhance our online grass roots efforts.  

Please feel free to drop Bob a note to say hello (bobpal@cdt.org).

