<TITLE>Policy Post 2.16 - Senator Burns Goes Online to Discuss Crypto Bill</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<PRE>
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
   _____ _____ _______
  / ____|  __ \__   __|   ____        ___               ____             __
 | |    | |  | | | |     / __ \____  / (_)______  __   / __ \____  _____/ /_
