<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT02-B07-112</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA095-001027-B012-9</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cdt.org:80/publications/ftc_xprivacy_112095.html 205.177.10.31 19970215011913 text/html 32943
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 15 Feb 1997 01:17:52 GMT
