<DOCNO>WT02-B07-114</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA095-001027-B024-328</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cdt.org:80/policy/healthpriv/jlg_111495_test.html 205.177.10.31 19970215002523 text/html 25953
