<TITLE>Triton Technology Job Opportunities</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="backgrnd.gif">
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="logo1.gif" ALT="TTI logo">

<A NAME="jobs"><h1>JOB OPPORTUNITIES!</h1></A>
<h2>For September-October, 1996
</h2>
<hr>
</center>
<h3> Triton Technology has positions available in:<p>
<A HREF="#software">SOFTWARE MANAGEMENT</A><p>

Triton is seeking a software development manager.  We're interested in candidates with experience in Windows programming (Win32 API), PC hardware and support
(both technical and sales).  We develop Windows software with Microsoft compilers and tools, so experience with Micsosoft's IDE, MFC C++ and DDK are helpful.  
Candidates with experience in the offshore search/survey industry will be given special consideration.
</h3>
<hr>

<h3>
Triton Technology, Inc. is an innovative engineering firm committed
to excellence in R&D and production of sonar and GPR
data acquisition and image processing products.  Our global leadership
and growth in government, commercial and scientific markets continue
to provide excellent employment opportunities.
<p>Triton Technology is located just south of Santa Cruz, California on 
the Monterey Bay.  We are a growing company and employ top-notch 
people.  Triton offers an excellent benefits package.  If you would like 
to submit a resume and apply for any of the positions below, simply 
e-mail <A HREF="mailto:hr@tritontech.com">hr@tritontech.com</A>.
You may attach your resume in either plain text or as a Microsoft Word document.  
Or you can snail-mail it to:</h3><p>
<pre>
<img src="enve.gif" alt="">
Triton Technology
% Human Resources
125 Westridge Dr.
Watsonville, CA  95076
</pre>
<hr>
<center>
