</UL>

<P><HR ALIGN=LEFT>Wednesday, February 26</P>

<UL>
  <LI>REFUGE: Dept. of Theatre &amp; Dance presents &quot;Refuge, An Unnatural
  History of Family and Place,&quot; by Terry Tempest Williams in the Main
  Theatre. For ticket information call 678-3975.
