<UL>
  <LI>RECRUITING: Peace Corps will be recruiting on campus in the UC, Room
  310E, from 12:00 p.m. to 1:00 p.m. For further information call David Graham
  at 678-2239.
</UL>

<P><HR ALIGN=LEFT>Wednesday, March 12</P>

<UL>
  <LI>DISCUSSION: Dr. S. Edward Stevens, topic and location to be determined
  at a later date.
  <LI>CAREER FAIR: Corporate and Government Career Fair, sponsored by Career
  &amp; Employment Services. UC, 3rd floor, 10:00 a.m. to 3:00 p.m. For more
